==English==
===Noun===
#A member of the Irish police force.
#Title of a male member of the force, eg ''Garda Joe Smith''. Female officers are correctly titled ''Ban Garda''
Plural: Gardaí.
The term "guards" is frequently used as a plural although this is incorrect.

===Etymology===
#From Irish ''Garda Síochána na hÉireann'' , meaning ''Guardians of the Peace of Ireland''